---
import Img from "../../assets/images/soldadura.jpg"
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro"
---
<div class="w-full 2xl:px-52 px-8 md:px-20 mt-10 flex flex-col items-start min-h-10/12 mb-1">
    <h1 class="text-xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-5">100% <br> Manufacturers</h1>
    <h2 class="text-base md:text-xl font-bold mb-5">Triaso manufacturers directly, we don´t have subcontractors</h2>
    <p class="font-bold text-gris5 text-sm md:text-lg mb-5 text-justify">No other asphalt plant manufacturer produces as many components 
        for its own equipment as we do. Unlike others, <strong class="text-black">we manufacture 
        directly without subcontractors</strong>, ensuring that every part meets 
        our strict quality standards.
        <br><br>
        This approach enables us to deliver <strong class="text-black">superior service, warranty,
         and direct support</strong> from both our manufacturing plant in Mexico 
         and USA. Unlike most brands, which produce only a few components
          and rely heavily on external suppliers, we manufacture and 
          assemble our equipment in-house.</p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 pt-5 w-full">
  <!-- Columna de texto -->
  <div class="font-bold text-grisT order-2 md:order-1">
    <h2 class="mb-5 text-base md:text-lg">Direct Attention from the Manufacturer</h2>
    <p class="text-grisP text-sm md:text-lg text-justify">At Triaso, you work directly with the manufacturer—no intermediaries or external sellers. We design and produce our equipment, guaranteeing top quality, competitive pricing, and personalized service. Our in-house manufacturing ensures unparalleled warranty coverage, rapid support, immediate spare parts availability, and customized solutions tailored to your needs.</p>
    <div class="flex gap-10 justify-center items-center mt-5 md:mt-20 pb-5">
      <button class="text-sm md:text-lg font-normal border-blueMain text-blueMain border rounded-full px-4 py-1 hover:bg-blueMainHover hover:text-white">Maintenance</button>
      <button class="text-sm md:text-lg font-normal border-redBg text-redBg border rounded-full px-4 py-1 hover:bg-redBgHover hover:text-white">Manufacture</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Columna de imagen (ajustada) -->
  <div class="w-full flex justify-center items-center order-1 md:order-2">
    <Image src={Img} alt="" class="rounded-2xl object-cover w-full h-auto max-h-[400px] md:max-h-none">
  </div>
</div>
</div>